<html>

<head>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css" data-inline="data-inline">
</head>

<body>
  <p class="preheader">

  </p>
  <div class="container">
    <header class="mcad-frame">
      MCAD
      ONLINE
      LEARNING
    </header>

    <main>
      <header class="email-header">
        <div class="header-image">ðŸš€</div>
        {{#if hasMultipleCourses }}
        <h1>
          Your Classes<br>
          are OPEN!
        </h1>
        {{else}}
        <h1>
          Your Class<br>
          is OPEN!
        </h1> {{/if}}
      </header>

      <p>Hello {{ firstName }},</p>

      <p>
        The following courses are now open on Canvas:
      </p>

      {{#each courses }}
      <div class="info-box course-info">
        <p><b>{{courseName}} ({{term}} {{year}})</b></p>
        <p>{{courseCode}} â€¢ {{ facultyFirstName }} {{ facultyLastName }} â€¢ {{credits}}</p>
        <p>{{startDate}} â€“ {{endDate}}</p>
      </div>
      {{/each}}

      <h2>Step 1</h2>

      <p><a class="button" href="https://canvas.mcad.edu">Login to Canvas</a>
      </p>

      <p>
        Make sure your MCAD Canvas account works by signing in to <a href="https://canvas.mcad.edu">canvas.mcad.edu</a>.
        If you cannot login, try <a href="https://password.mcad.edu/index.php?selfservice=forgotpw">resetting your
          password</a> or contacting the friendly folks at the <a
          href="https://intranet.mcad.edu/department/help-desk">MCAD Help Desk</a>:
      </p>

      <div class="contact-info">
        <p><a href="mailto:helpdesk@mcad.edu">helpdesk@mcad.edu</a></p>
        <p><a href="tel:6128743666">612-874-3666</a></p>
      </div>

      <h3>Will all of my classes be using Canvas this semester?</h3>

      <p>
        <em>Most classes will be using Canvas LMS,</em> but some faculty have opted to continue using the legacy
        Blackboard system at <a href="https://learn.mcad.edu">https://learn.mcad.edu</a>. Faculty will let you know
        about their plans. You will also see a message in your Canvas class redirecting you to Blackboard if this is the
        case.
      </p>


      <h2>Step 2</h2>

      <p><a class="button" href="https://canvas.mcad.edu/orientation">Begin Canvas Orientation</a>
      </p>

      <p>
        If you're new to Canvas <a href="https://canvas.mcad.edu/orientation">watch the Canvas
          Orientation</a>.</p>

      <p>
        This orientation will take you about an hour. It includes an overview of Canvas,
        tips for setting up notifications, checking grades, getting the app, and more.
      </p>

      <h2>Step 3</h2>

      <p><a class="button" href="https://canvas.mcad.edu">Explore Your Canvas Classroom</a>
      </p>

      <p>Some things to do:</p>

      <ul>
        <li>Review the syllabus</li>
        <li>Find your remote class meeting link (it's probably with the syllabus)</li>
        <li>Check out what's planned for the first week of class</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Questions? Need Help?</h2>

      <dl class="key-value">
        <dt class="key">Trouble logging in?</dt>
        <dd class="value">
          <a href="mailto:helpdesk@mcad.edu">helpdesk@mcad.edu</a>
        </dd>

        <dt class="key">Questions about Canvas?</dt>
        <dd class="value">
          <a href="mailto:online@mcad.edu">online@mcad.edu</a>
        </dd>

        <dt class="key">Something else?</dt>
        <dd class="value">
          Try the <a href="https://intranet.mcad.edu/directory">MCAD Intranet Directory</a>.
        </dd>

      </dl>
      <p>Have a great semester!</p>
    </main>
  </div>
</body>

</html>
